{
  "stem": "5103.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of them, as they were walking past, you know, the compartments, as they were walking by, one of them-- I was a blonde girl, and I had light colored eyes-- one of them just put his hand on my head and said, [NON-ENGLISH], which means like a nice Aryan girl.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I just looked down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I was a child, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was told not to say, not to smile, not to look.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it stuck with me, because what he said-- because I knew I was a Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But for him to say that and sort of stroke my head as well, it was quite awful.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, because [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] prior to this-- I've skipped a little here-- there were times when we had walked in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, I was issued with a star-- a yellow star with black [NON-ENGLISH] written on it-- and my mother and my father as well.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I knew this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were incidents, like while we were walking in the city, Mom and Dad-- going back a little bit, before I went with this man.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now I'm coming back a little bit, backtracking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were walking in the city one day, and I had my star, and my mother had my star-- had her star.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was a tremendous shooting in the city going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were shooting at non-Jewish men and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were just men in general they wanted to round up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And these two men were-- we had been to see my, somebody, my father in hospital or my grandfather in hospital.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he-- my mother said to me, I hope they don't run.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
